name: Master Timekeeper
description:
I've been awake for days, so we out living life in the night
Pray to God, man I hope I don't die in the night.

- Spiders can show up during periods of darkness, depression, and grief.

- Spiders teach you to reflect on your past spiritual lessons to help you plan for the future.
They can alert you when you are stuck in the past, or jumping forward in the future.

- Spiritually, spiders show us the importance of birth, growth, death, and rebirth, spinning a web of evolution and spiritual transformation.
